                <note>The name of this animal is explained by <persName ref="https://syriaca.org/person/472">Elias of <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/142">Nisibis</placeName></persName> in his <ref>Lexidion</ref> by <foreign xml:lang="ar">خَرانِقُ (فرانق؟) الأَسَدِ</foreign>, and in <bibl>Add. 7203</bibl> by <foreign xml:lang="ar">فراس (فرانق؟) الاسدَ</foreign>.</note>
              </msItem>
